00:16:05,340 --> 00:16:07,260
The invasion of Persia. Okay?

269
00:16:07,380 --> 00:16:09,800
Now, originally his father,

270
00:16:10,020 --> 00:16:11,220
Philip II,

271
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:14,880
his dream was a unified Greek world.

272
00:16:15,040 --> 00:16:17,520
Okay? What we call Hellenistic.

273
00:16:19,060 --> 00:16:20,740
Okay? Or the Hellenic world.

274
00:16:21,300 --> 00:16:24,340
Because remember, at this point,
you have these Greek -Polish

