00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:46,660
Okay? So he's expanding
his father's vision.

281
00:16:46,920 --> 00:16:49,820
So he's landing, he lands in Anatolia,

282
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:52,800
which is like modern -day Turkey,
with this massive invasion force.

283
00:16:53,100 --> 00:16:55,180
Okay? And he's going
