311
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:30,880
Okay? The war is over.

312
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:32,400
It doesn't cost us anything.

313
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:36,100
Okay? The satraps refuse this plan

