326
00:19:18,260 --> 00:19:22,300
Okay? But then at the last minute,
a man named Plitus the Black,

327
00:19:23,260 --> 00:19:25,200
Plitus the Black,

328
00:19:25,420 --> 00:19:28,540
comes running in and he slashes,

329
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:31,060
he cuts off the satraps' arm.

330
00:19:31,060 --> 00:19:32,860
Thus saving Alexander's life.

331
00:19:33,120 --> 00:19:37,100
All right? So at this point,
there are two individuals

