336
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:52,620
Okay? And Plitus the Black, who

337
00:19:52,620 --> 00:19:55,640
saved Alexander's life in battle. And

338
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:58,220
both of these men were individuals

339
00:19:58,220 --> 00:20:02,380
promoted heavily by his
father for their talent.

340
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:05,300
Okay? So basically, it was his
father's man that saved Alexander.

341
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:09,400
So you would think Alexander would
be very grateful to these men.

342
00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:13,120
Right? Unfortunately,

343
00:20:13,180 --> 00:20:14,540
he would end up killing both men.

344
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:18,940
And this would forever change
the course of his life.

345
00:20:19,140 --> 00:20:21,240
Okay? All right. So,

346
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:25,020
after the Battle of Granaticus,

347
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:27,700
Menna Rhodes was given

348
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:32,620
complete freedom to do what he wanted.

349
00:20:33,140 --> 00:20:35,980
So Menna Rhodes tried to stop Alexander.

350
00:20:37,300 --> 00:20:40,800
And when he realized he couldn't do it
because Alexander's army was too powerful,

351
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:44,220
Menna Rhodes set sail for Greece.

352
00:20:44,460 --> 00:20:46,780
He was hoping to bribe Athens and

353
00:20:46,780 --> 00:20:50,480
Sparta to join the war and
rebel against Alexander.

354
00:20:51,060 --> 00:20:53,060
And here, something that happens.

355
00:20:53,860 --> 00:20:55,520
And Alexander gets really lucky.

356
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:57,240
Okay? And we will find this in his life.

357
00:20:57,340 --> 00:20:58,960
He gets very lucky a lot of times.

358
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:03,000
And what is it that happens when
Menna Rhodes sets sail for Greece?

359
00:21:03,320 --> 00:21:07,860
About to, and he's about to unite the
Greeks and rebel against Alexander.

360
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:11,300
And remember, Athens and Sparta at
this point really hates Alexander.

361
00:21:11,980 --> 00:21:15,460
So what happens? He dies.

362
00:21:15,600 --> 00:21:17,080
Okay? He gets sick and he dies.

363
00:21:17,300 --> 00:21:18,920
And when Menna Rhodes dies,

364
00:21:19,300 --> 00:21:22,580
